metadata.name: As the darkness envelops my soul.
metadata.description: This collection features digital artworks created with algorithms and technology that explore the various facets of darkness, including its presence in the human soul and its role in the natural world. Through a range of styles and techniques, the collection delves into themes of isolation, despair, fear, secrecy, ignorance, and hidden knowledge, offering a unique and thought-provoking exploration of the concept of darkness and its place in the human experience.
